{"tid":1923102,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"旗艦手機相機 VS. DC仔相機","createTime":"2020-03-13T02:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T17:02:45.000Z","uid":180161,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"963e174a573b65e195be3375495236d7e18c145a","tid":1923102,"uid":180161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:00:45.000Z","msg":"小弟想買新手機，一直都諗住要影相最好嘅手機一定係要旗艦機，所以都傾向買旗艦<br />\n<br />\n但係諗諗下，我淨係一年一次旅行先影一次相，平時都冇嘢好影，又唔玩手機遊戲<br />\n<br />\n所以諗緊與其咁貴買部旗艦機，不如$3000左右買部中階機，再加部DC仔畀我旅行專用，咁樣不但慳番錢之餘，影出嚟相質素可能好過旗艦。<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位點睇？邊樣影相質素好？（不論日夜拍）"},{"pid":"8b617ebe182af04c7daa7b07b0fcb6ad4a865167","tid":1923102,"uid":196924,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:05:10.000Z","msg":"一年用一次都仲特登買DC仔, 咩邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088ae31e0927e1f27aa9b598bd0471f4f344c097","tid":1923102,"uid":125488,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:08:29.000Z","msg":"一年影一次 買黎把撚"},{"pid":"3c5da6dc3e03dc84ae683a1fbf0be9eecf44ac6c","tid":1923102,"uid":56115,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:09:37.000Z","msg":"一年一次問朋友借好過啦，小心啲用，事後請佢食餐飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4467a647448aa9248de74ad887008079b81c24f","tid":1923102,"uid":282053,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:10:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L25zdvdEOQg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL25zdvdEOQg&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=7c21d134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L25zdvdEOQg</a><br />\n此post已完"},{"pid":"d595612dafd4196520176acfff6cbdbf008eae71","tid":1923102,"uid":43520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:16:31.000Z","msg":"還有一點, 你影完的相會點用點處理?<br />\n如果只是放上fb, 在手機睇相的話<br />\n點解唔直接用手機影?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{